casebody.data:
Tuesday, March 1, 1994

MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

94-272. State ex rel. Miller v. Ohio Adult Parole Auth.

In Mandamus. This cause originated in this court on the filing of a complaint for a writ of mandamus. Upon consideration of relator’s application to dismiss,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that said application be, and the same is hereby, granted, effective February 28, 1994.

ACCORDINGLY, IT IS FURTHER ORDERED by the court that this cause be, and hereby is, dismissed.
